
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home Page";
}

@section styles {
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/Css/Pages/AboutUs.css" />
}

<div class="container">
    <h1 class="page-heading">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-newspaper"></i>
        About Us
    </h1>

    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12">
                    <p class="about-us-content">
                        We founded the NOSBlog web site that is not limited to anyone, anyone can express their own opinion. The purpose of creating the web is for people to share difficulties in life, work, study or joy, .... The web is not limited to age, although anyone can register. If you don't have an account, log in if you already have an account.
                    </p>
                    <p class="about-us-content">
                        The Web can be accessed from Internet-connected devices, such as personal computers, tablets, and smartphones. After registering and logging in to an account, users can view or post their own funny moments on the web to share with everyone.
                    </p>
                    <p class="about-us-content">
                        We want to create a healthy website where people can visit or share their lessons, experiences, sadness or joy. Let people speak out, reduce troubles in life. And that is also our goal when creating the NOSBlog website.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>